            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the belief that getting ahead isn't available to you. The script targets the inherited sense that effort is endless, the goal always moves, and enough is always just out of reach."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
          { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works" } }], "text": "how EFT tapping works" },
          { "type": "text", "text": " first." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "The practice" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Karate chop" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I carry the belief that we never get ahead, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though it feels like effort never lands and enough never stays, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though this belief has been in my family for longer than I've been alive, I am open to releasing it now." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tapping round" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " We never get ahead." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I work hard and it goes nowhere." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " There's always another bill, another setback." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I expect it to stay hard." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Getting ahead feels like something that happens to other people." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm waiting for the rug to be pulled." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I feel defeated before I've started." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I wonder if this is just the way it is for people like me." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I can see where this belief came from." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Getting ahead is allowed for me, not just for others." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Effort can build into something real and lasting." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I am open to a different result this time." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I release the expectation of struggle." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I allow money to stay and build." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I am the person who changes this." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Ahead is possible. Ahead is mine." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times." }]
      },
